### Degenerate baseline check

Shuffled Morgan FP and random continuous vectors produce delta = {{ c.morgan_fp_shuffled.delta | signed }}
and {{ c.random_continuous.delta | signed }} respectively — identical to real Morgan FP
({{ c.morgan_fp.delta | signed }}). Adding ANY extra features to Ridge produces the same tiny
positive delta due to the mechanical effect of additional input dimensions. The "real" drug
feature signal is indistinguishable from noise.

